Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:36.39,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Rumbling, Rumbling, it's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.52,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Rumbling, Rumbling
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:42.48,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Beware
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.57,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}coming for you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:56.58,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}all I ever wanted to do was do right things
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:59.08,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I never wanted to be the king,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:02.09,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I swear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:06.34,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}all I ever wanted to do was save your life
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:09.05,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I never wanted to grab a knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:12.10,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I swear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:16.93,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}tearless, fearless,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.90,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}burning, burning
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.94,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}you tell me what have I missed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:26.78,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}still wandering in the deep mist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:32.62,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}if I lose it all, slip and fall
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:35.54,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I will never look away
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:41.79,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}if I lose it all, lose it all, lose it all
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:45.38,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}if I lose it all outside the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:48.76,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}live to die another day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:54.47,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I don't want anything I'm just here to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.02,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Beware
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:59.14,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Rumbling, Rumbling, it's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.81,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Rumbling, Rumbling
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:36.39,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地鳴 地鳴 隆隆而至
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.52,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地鳴 地鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:42.48,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.57,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為你而來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:56.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只想做正確之事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:59.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我並不想稱王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:02.09,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:06.34,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只想拯救你的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:09.05,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我並不想拿起利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:12.10,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:16.93,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不流淚 不畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.90,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃燒 燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.94,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你告訴我 我錯過了太多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:26.78,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仍在濃霧中彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:32.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若我失去一切 墜入深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:35.54,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我決不會逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:41.79,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若我失去一切 失去一切 失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:45.38,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若我在牆外失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:48.76,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我定將向死而生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:54.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我本不願立於此處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.02,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:59.14,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地鳴 地鳴 隆隆而至
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.81,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地鳴 地鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:13.20,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}鉄の弾が 正義の証明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:15.87,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}貫けば 英雄に近づいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:18.58,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}その目を閉じて 触れてみれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:23.17,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}同じ形 同じ体温の悪魔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:26.54,ed-jp,,0,0,1,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}僕はダメで あいつはいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:29.26,ed-jp,,0,0,1,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}そこに壁があっただけなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.88,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}生まれてしまった 運命嘆くな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:35.76,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}僕らはみんな 自由なんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:41.02,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}鳥のように 羽があれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:46.36,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}どこへだって行けるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:50.44,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}帰る場所が なければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:22:55.87,ed-jp,,0,0,1,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}きっとどこへも行けない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.91,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ただただ生きるのは嫌だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:06.42,ed-jp-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}世界は残酷だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.42,0:23:11.97,ed-jp-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}それでも君を愛すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.97,0:23:17.26,ed-jp-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}なにを犠牲にしても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:21.98,ed-jp-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}それでも君を守るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:27.27,ed-jp-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}間違いだとしても 疑ったりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:34.11,ed-jp-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}正しさとは自分のこと 強く信じることだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:10.49,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:13.20,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}鋼鐵彈丸 即為正義之證
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:15.87,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}貫穿一切 便是英雄之舉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:18.58,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}閉上眼 去觸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:23.17,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}外貌相似 體溫相同 同為惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:26.54,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}為什麼我不行 他就可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:29.26,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唯有一牆之隔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.88,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}既已誕生 便不要哀嘆命運
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:35.76,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我們人人自由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:41.02,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只要像鳥一般 羽翼豐滿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:46.36,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}便能無所不往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:50.44,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}但若沒有歸處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:22:55.87,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}便無處能去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.91,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只是一味厭惡人生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:06.42,ed-cn-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}世界如此殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.42,0:23:11.97,ed-cn-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}但我依舊愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.97,0:23:17.26,ed-cn-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即便犧牲一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:21.98,ed-cn-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}也要將你守護
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:27.27,ed-cn-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即便錯誤 也決不懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:34.11,ed-cn-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}堅信自己 即為正道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:35.93,ed-cn-2,,0,0,0,,
